title: Timucuan Ecological & Historic Preserve: Theodore Roosevelt Area
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     History & Culture     Places     Theodore Roosevelt Area                 Theodore Roosevelt Area      The Theodore Roosevelt Area is a 600-acre natural treasure of hardwood forest, wetlands, and scrub vegetation. It is also rich in cultural history. Visiting the Theodore Roosevelt Area Nature and History      The hiking trails are open and waiting for you. NPS Photo/Stankiewicz
